Introduction

Taerae is a South Korean singer and rapper under Yue Hua Entertainment.

On January 3, 2022, Taerae was revealed as the second member of Yue Hua Entertainment's upcoming boy group TEMPEST. He debuted as a member of the group on March 2, 2022, with the release of their first mini album titled "It's ME, It's WE".
